{"title":"Updated Bontrager Flatline MTB Shoes protect your toes and breathe more freely","link":"https://bikerumor.com/2021/11/05/updated-bontrager-flatline-mtb-shoes-protect-your-toes-and-breathe-more-freely/","date":1636116474000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/05080238/bontrager-flatline-mtb-shoe-camo.jpg\" data-fancybox=\"\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"534\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/05080238/bontrager-flatline-mtb-shoe-camo-800x534.jpg\" alt=\"bontrager flatline mtb shoes camo\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/05080238/bontrager-flatline-mtb-shoe-camo-800x534.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/05080238/bontrager-flatline-mtb-shoe-camo-297x198.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/05080238/bontrager-flatline-mtb-shoe-camo-120x80.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/05080238/bontrager-flatline-mtb-shoe-camo-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/05080238/bontrager-flatline-mtb-shoe-camo-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/05080238/bontrager-flatline-mtb-shoe-camo.jpg 1600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"></a><header></header><p>Support us! BikeRumor may earn a small commission from affiliate links in this article. <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/privacy\" target=\"_blank\">Learn more</a>.</p></div><div role=\"main\"><article id=\"post-277582\" role=\"article\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/BlogPosting\"><section itemprop=\"text\"><p>Bontrager has updated their <strong><a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=el&amp;merchant_id=0d15472d-796a-41f7-afb4-32437118891b&amp;website_id=3407ca35-0b50-44fe-aeb1-9ab6a93bba54&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.trekbikes.com%2Fus%2Fen_US%2Fbike-clothing%2Fcycling-shoes%2Fmountain-bike-shoes%2Fmens-mountain-bike-shoes%2Fbontrager-flatline-mountain-bike-shoe%2Fp%2F34790%2F\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Flatline MTB Shoes</a></strong> for flat pedal riders, improving durability, breathability, and toe protection. The shoe retains the Vibram outsole seen on previous iterations but gets a highly perforated upper that gives the shoe a polka dot aesthetic and allows the wearer’s feet to breathe.</p><h2>Bontrager Flatline MTB Shoes</h2><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/05081438/Flatline-Shoe_lifestyle_16.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/05081438/Flatline-Shoe_lifestyle_16.jpg\" alt=\"bontrager flatline mtb shoe camo upper perforations\" width=\"1600\" height=\"1067\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/05081438/Flatline-Shoe_lifestyle_16.jpg 1600w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/05081438/Flatline-Shoe_lifestyle_16-297x198.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/05081438/Flatline-Shoe_lifestyle_16-800x534.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/05081438/Flatline-Shoe_lifestyle_16-120x80.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/05081438/Flatline-Shoe_lifestyle_16-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/05081438/Flatline-Shoe_lifestyle_16-1536x1024.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\"></a></p><p>Despite the massive increase in the use of perforations across the sides and above the toe box, the new <strong><a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=el&amp;merchant_id=0d15472d-796a-41f7-afb4-32437118891b&amp;website_id=3407ca35-0b50-44fe-aeb1-9ab6a93bba54&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.trekbikes.com%2Fus%2Fen_US%2Fbike-clothing%2Fcycling-shoes%2Fmountain-bike-shoes%2Fmens-mountain-bike-shoes%2Fbontrager-flatline-mountain-bike-shoe%2Fp%2F34790%2F\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Bontrager Flatline shoe</a></strong> ends up with a much more casual aesthetic thanks to the more understated colorways now available with black laces only. The only eye-catcher is the bright yellow Vibram logo at the heel, indicating the rubber compound seen at the outsole.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/05080247/bontrager-flatline-mtb-shoe-vibram-outsole.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/05080247/bontrager-flatline-mtb-shoe-vibram-outsole.jpg\" alt=\"bontrager flatline vibram outsole pattern\" width=\"1600\" height=\"1067\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/05080247/bontrager-flatline-mtb-shoe-vibram-outsole.jpg 1600w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/05080247/bontrager-flatline-mtb-shoe-vibram-outsole-297x198.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/05080247/bontrager-flatline-mtb-shoe-vibram-outsole-800x534.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/05080247/bontrager-flatline-mtb-shoe-vibram-outsole-120x80.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/05080247/bontrager-flatline-mtb-shoe-vibram-outsole-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/05080247/bontrager-flatline-mtb-shoe-vibram-outsole-1536x1024.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\"></a></p><p>Underneath, the Bontrager Flatline outsole remains unchanged. In the pedal zone, Vibram rubber is shaped into a lattice of textured low-profile squares with chamfered edges, while the heel and toe regions get a deeper, more aggressive zig-zag pattern designed to enhance grip in these areas for hiking back up the trail.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/05080242/bontrager-flatline-mtb-shoe-sole-toe-region-hiking-grip.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/05080242/bontrager-flatline-mtb-shoe-sole-toe-region-hiking-grip.jpg\" alt=\"bontrager flatline toe tread pattern\" width=\"1600\" height=\"1067\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/05080242/bontrager-flatline-mtb-shoe-sole-toe-region-hiking-grip.jpg 1600w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/05080242/bontrager-flatline-mtb-shoe-sole-toe-region-hiking-grip-297x198.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/05080242/bontrager-flatline-mtb-shoe-sole-toe-region-hiking-grip-800x534.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/05080242/bontrager-flatline-mtb-shoe-sole-toe-region-hiking-grip-120x80.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/05080242/bontrager-flatline-mtb-shoe-sole-toe-region-hiking-grip-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/05080242/bontrager-flatline-mtb-shoe-sole-toe-region-hiking-grip-1536x1024.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\"></a></p><p>Something you can’t tell from the pictures is that Bontrager has used their new InForm Performance last in the production of the new Flatline shoe. This is said to deliver a relaxed fit with a flatter foot position, perhaps better for those who dislike a high arch at the instep. Under the sole is a shock-absorbing EVA midsole said to reduce fatigue.</p><div id=\"attachment_277593\"><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/05084023/bontrager-flatline-camo-shoe.jpg\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-277593\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/05084023/bontrager-flatline-camo-shoe.jpg\" alt=\"new strong, synthetic perforated upper materials \" width=\"1600\" height=\"1067\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/05084023/bontrager-flatline-camo-shoe.jpg 1600w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/05084023/bontrager-flatline-camo-shoe-297x198.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/05084023/bontrager-flatline-camo-shoe-800x534.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/05084023/bontrager-flatline-camo-shoe-120x80.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/05084023/bontrager-flatline-camo-shoe-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/05084023/bontrager-flatline-camo-shoe-1536x1024.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\"></a></p><p id=\"caption-attachment-277593\">Laces can be tucked away into an elasticated tab on the tongue to stop them from getting caught</p></div><p>Bontrager has further updated the Flatline with a reinforced toe box, in order to better protect your digits next time you toe punt a rock or stump.</p><div id=\"attachment_277591\"><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/05081434/bontrager-flatline-shoe-casey-brown-northsore-jump.jpg\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-277591\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/05081434/bontrager-flatline-shoe-casey-brown-northsore-jump.jpg\" alt=\"casey brown bontrager flatline\" width=\"1600\" height=\"1067\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/05081434/bontrager-flatline-shoe-casey-brown-northsore-jump.jpg 1600w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/05081434/bontrager-flatline-shoe-casey-brown-northsore-jump-297x198.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/05081434/bontrager-flatline-shoe-casey-brown-northsore-jump-800x534.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/05081434/bontrager-flatline-shoe-casey-brown-northsore-jump-120x80.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/05081434/bontrager-flatline-shoe-casey-brown-northsore-jump-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/05081434/bontrager-flatline-shoe-casey-brown-northsore-jump-1536x1024.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\"></a></p><p id=\"caption-attachment-277591\">Trek free-rider Casey Brown sending a North Shore gap in her Bontrager Flatline MTB Shoes</p></div><h3>Pricing &amp; Availability</h3><p>The <strong><a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=el&amp;merchant_id=0d15472d-796a-41f7-afb4-32437118891b&amp;website_id=3407ca35-0b50-44fe-aeb1-9ab6a93bba54&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.trekbikes.com%2Fus%2Fen_US%2Fbike-clothing%2Fcycling-shoes%2Fmountain-bike-shoes%2Fmens-mountain-bike-shoes%2Fbontrager-flatline-mountain-bike-shoe%2Fp%2F34790%2F\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Bontrager Flatline MTB Shoes</a></strong> are available now from Trek dealers with an MSRP of $139.99 USD in unisex sizing. Worth noting is the 30-Day Unconditional Guarantee, which gives riders 30 days to love their purchase. If they don’t, Bontrager will take it back.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/05081430/bontrager-flatline-black-grey-camo-options.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/05081430/bontrager-flatline-black-grey-camo-options.jpg\" alt=\"bontrager flatline 2022 colorways\" width=